desc: Duff's Vintage Collection offers many "one of a kind" vintage and classic antique items from around the United States. We offer vintage road signs, neon signs, gas pumps, bicycles, pedal toys and other unique items. These items are great for accent decorations in stores, restaurants, bars, businesses & homes.

layout.text: Classic collectibles, signs, bicycles, toys, gas pumps, furniture, pictures, oil & gas memorabilia and unique vintage gifts
